1
00:00:03,874 --> 00:00:08,693
Mr. Hall:
Ha ha ha...ha ha ha.
I oughta have this framed.

2
00:00:08,819 --> 00:00:12,080
My last bill from Princeton.

3
00:00:12,910 --> 00:00:16,020
And I thought
we were celebrating the fact that
I actually graduated.

4
00:00:16,104 --> 00:00:17,563
I always knew
you'd be able to graduate.

5
00:00:17,647 --> 00:00:20,759
What I didn't know was whether
I would be able to pay for it.

6
00:00:20,867 --> 00:00:21,910
[Chuckles]

7
00:00:22,093 --> 00:00:23,478
Your mom...

8
00:00:24,005 --> 00:00:25,883
She'd be so proud of you.

9
00:00:26,718 --> 00:00:28,299
You always say that.

10
00:00:28,721 --> 00:00:30,373
I'm so proud of you.

11
00:00:30,691 --> 00:00:32,403
Always was.

12
00:00:34,784 --> 00:00:36,509
Come on, Dad.
You're gonna cry.

13
00:00:36,593 --> 00:00:39,703
[Laughs]
You wanna be embarrassed?

14
00:00:40,124 --> 00:00:42,925
You got it. Ahhh.

15
00:00:48,149 --> 00:00:49,448
[Chuckle]

16
00:00:50,008 --> 00:00:52,349
Look, um, don't party
too hard tonight.

17
00:00:52,427 --> 00:00:54,553
Your grandmother wants a picture
of you getting that sheepskin.

18
00:00:54,656 --> 00:00:57,060
And it'd be nice if you didn't
look completely hung over.

19
00:00:57,144 --> 00:00:58,348
Ooh, no, don't worry.

20
00:00:58,348 --> 00:01:01,739
I've had enough alcohol
in the past week to last me
another four years.

21
00:01:01,846 --> 00:01:04,787
- Good...I think.
- [Laughs]

22
00:01:04,871 --> 00:01:08,510
<i># Yo pretty ladies around the world #</i>

23
00:01:08,638 --> 00:01:12,853
<i># Got a weird thing to show you
So tell all the boys and girls #</i>

24
